Rattrap:




The timing was up. The CR chamber's door opened, and Rattrap stepped 
out. The first thing he saw was a female scorpion (Solo), drenched in 
mech fluid, attemting to fix herself. 

"Slag," he said. "Who scrabbled with you, sister?" He wasn't aware 
that he was in Predacon hands yet.
